OL,5, A bus driver has been praised for      
OL,6, helping a woman and her three children 
OL,7, flee from an abusive man in the area.  
OL,9,FKyle Caswell, 18, from Swindon, said he
OL,10,Fwas at the end of his route when he was
OL,11,Fstopped by a woman and her children.   
OL,13,FHe said the woman told him she had been
OL,14,Ftrying to avoid an abusive ex-partner  
OL,15,Fwho was nearby and looking for her.    
OL,17,FMr Caswell obtained permission from his
OL,18,Fsupervisor to take them to a safer     
OL,19,Flocation across town and Swindon Bus   
OL,20,FCompany said it was very proud of him. 
